quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  57,12,"√Ďande nji'oytaa gooŇč…óin…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen e gooŇč…óin…ďe rew…ďe …ďeen, hara annoora ma…ď…ďe yaara ye'eso ma…ď…ďe e √Īaamo ma…ď…ďe (…ďe mbi'anee): "Weltaare mon hannde ko Aljannaaji, …ói can…ói ilata senngo ley mum, ko on duumotoo…ďe ndeer ton". Ko …óum woni malal mawngal ngal."
  57,13,"√Ďalnde naafiqii…ďe wor…ďe …ďeen e naafiqii…ďe rew…ďe …ďen mbi'anoyta gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďeen: "kabbee min, min njalbinora annoora mon on". ∆Āe mbi'anee : "Yiltoree …ďaawo mon, …óa…ď…ďoyon annoora". Heedo wa…óee hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ngo damal ngal yurmeende woni e nder mum, …ďaawo maggal noon, ko lepte woni e bannge mum."
  57,14,"Hi…ďe nodda …ďe : "E min ngondaano e mon?" ∆Āe mbi'a : "Ko non nhoniri. Ko woni tun, on fitinno ko'e mon, habbitani…óon [gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen bone], cikkiti…óon, yelaaji hodi on haa yamiroore Allah nden ari. Hodoowo on hodi on e mo∆ī∆īere Allah ndeen."
  57,15,"Hannde noon, on nja…ďantaake coktor…óum wonaa e …ďeen yeddu…ďe. Depporde mon nden ko ka Yiite : ko ngen woni ko hanndu…óon. Nge bonii ruttorde."
  57,16,"E yontaani gooŇč…óii…ďe …ďen nde …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen dee∆īirta jantoore Allah nden e kon ko jippii immorde e goonga? Hara …ďe wa'aani wa …ďeen okkanoo…ďe defte …ďen ko adii, dumunna on juutani …ďeen, …ďer…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen njo'ori, ko …óuu…óunoo e ma…ď…ďe ko ko faasiqii…ďe."
  57,17,"Nganndee pellet, Allah wuurnitay lesdi ndiin …ďaawo ndi yo'orii. GooŇč…óii Min …ďannginiranii on aayeeje …óeen, fii no haqqiliron."
  57,18,"Pellet, sakkotoo…ďe (jaw…óe mum …ďeen) ka wor…ďe e ka rew…ďe …ďe √Īami Allah √Īamaande labaande, …ďe sowanoyte (mbarjaari) hara no woodani …ďe njo…ďdi mawndi."